'''2015年埃塞俄比亞大選'''於5月24日舉行，選出[[联邦议会_(埃塞俄比亚)|聯邦議會]]人民代表院及地方議會議員。<ref>{{cite web |last= |first= |date=2015 |title=African election calendar 2015 |url=http://www.content.eisa.org.za/old-page/african-election-calendar-2015 |publisher=Electoral Institute for Sustainable Democracy in Africa |location= |access-date=2015-02-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150227192613/http://www.content.eisa.org.za/old-page/african-election-calendar-2015 |archivedate=2015-02-27 }}</ref>結果[[埃塞俄比亚人民革命民主阵线|埃塞俄比亚人民革命民主阵线]]（EPRDF）贏得人民代表院547席中的500席。人民代表院其餘議席由埃革陣的盟友取得。<ref>[http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/jun/22/ethiopias-ruling-party-win-clean-sweep-general-election Ethiopia's ruling party wins by landslide in general election] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/jun/22/ethiopias-ruling-party-win-clean-sweep-general-election |date=20160723230744 }}, The Guardian, 22 June 2015</ref>

==選舉制度==
人民代表院的547個議席由單議席選區選出，採用[[簡單多數制|簡單多數制]]。<ref>[http://www.ipu.org/parline-e/reports/2107_B.htm Electoral system] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20130113030458/http://www.ipu.org/parline-e/reports/2107_B.htm |date=2013-01-13 }} IPU</ref>選舉結果於投票結束後一個月宣佈。<ref>[http://www.reuters.com/article/us-ethiopia-election-idUSKBN0OC1KS20150527 Ethiopia's ruling party sweeps parliament in early vote results] {{Wayback|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-ethiopia-election-idUSKBN0OC1KS20150527 |date=20170218064427 }}, 2015-05-27.</ref>反對派認為本次選舉不民主。<ref>[https://www.yahoo.com/news/ethiopia-opposition-says-elections-undemocratic-disgrace-220257213.html Ethiopia opposition says elections an 'undemocratic disgrace'] {{Wayback|url=https://www.yahoo.com/news/ethiopia-opposition-says-elections-undemocratic-disgrace-220257213.html |date=20160922174915 }}, 2015-05-29.</ref>

在Gimbo Gawata選區的投票由於埃革陣與一位獨立參選人發生衝突，延至6月14日舉行。<ref>[http://www.fanabc.com/english/index.php/ethiopian-election/item/3194-polls-to-open-in-bonga-tomorrow Polls to open in Bonga tomorrow] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fanabc.com/english/index.php/ethiopian-election/item/3194-polls-to-open-in-bonga-tomorrow |date=20150702203936 }} FBC, 13 June 2015</ref>

==過程==
共有1,828人角逐人民代表院的547席。<ref>[http://www.electionethiopia.org/en/ 2015 General Election Poletical parties Candidatures] {{Wayback|url=http://www.electionethiopia.org/en/ |date=20170531161656 }} National Electoral Board of Ethiopia</ref>

